---
// Standalone 404 — deliberately NOT using Base.astro: a 404 must not carry
// canonical/hreflang (it is not an alias of any page), and needs noindex.
// Its presence in dist/ also disables Cloudflare Pages' SPA fallback, which
// used to serve the homepage as HTTP 200 for ANY unknown path (that is how
// the malformed /ja/github.com URL got crawled and surfaced by Google).
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <title>Claude Pulse — Page not found</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Source Sans 3", system-ui, sans-serif;
        max-width: 40em;
        margin: 4em auto;
        padding: 0 1em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #1a1a1b;
        background: #faf9f0;
      }
      a {
        color: #d97757;
      }
      h1 {
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>404 — Page not found</h1>
    <p>
      This page doesn't exist on Claude Pulse. The latest Anthropic / Claude
      updates are at <a href="/">claude-pulse.chatbot.tw</a>, and older entries
      live in the monthly archive linked from the home page.
    </p>
    <p>找不到這個頁面。最新動態請見<a href="/zh-TW/">首頁</a>，歷史條目在首頁下方的月份彙整。</p>
  </body>
</html>
